# A static deploy serves EVERY file it ships — anything listed here would
# otherwise be downloadable from the live site.

# Dev tooling — the app never loads these (app/ and game_rules/ .mjs are the app).
node_modules
temporary screenshots
serve.mjs
screenshot.mjs
package.json
package-lock.json
tsconfig.base.json
.claude

# The monorepo the multiplayer build lives in. The static site is still served
# from the repo root and loads none of it; shipping TypeScript source to a
# static host would just be dead weight. Removed when Stage C flips the site
# over to the Next.js app.
packages
apps

# Asset-generation scripts and their source sheet.
brand_assets/_gen_*.py
brand_assets/_slice_dog_v2.py
brand_assets/dog-sprite*.png
brand_assets/style-guide.html

# Desktop font source. Only the .woff2 ships — a live site serving the raw .otf
# is handing out the installable font, which no foundry EULA allows.
AMORIA-BF64a2f6809ce9e.otf

# Internal docs — not part of the product.
PRD.md
CLAUDE.md
Amygdala Wireframe.dc.html
